bonfyre-queue

Usage:
  bonfyre-queue enqueue <queue-file> <job-slug> <payload-path> [--source NAME] [--priority N]
  bonfyre-queue list <queue-file>
  bonfyre-queue claim <queue-file> [--worker NAME]
  bonfyre-queue complete <queue-file> <job-id>
  bonfyre-queue fail <queue-file> <job-id>
  bonfyre-queue stats <queue-file>
